WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
الحمد بالله رب العالمين

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:07.000
الرحمن الرحيم

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:10.000
ملك يوم الدين

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:14.000
إياك نعبد وإياك نستعين

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:17.000
اهدن الصراة المستقيم

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:21.000
صراة الذين أنأنت عليهم

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:24.000
غير المغضوب عليهم

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:36.860
يا ربكم الذين

00:00:36.860 --> 00:00:39.860
عليكم ورحمة الله وبركاته

00:00:39.860 --> 00:00:42.860
بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم الحمد لله رب العالمين

00:00:42.860 --> 00:00:44.860
وبه نستعين ونصلي ونسلم

00:00:44.860 --> 00:00:46.860
على أفضل الخلق أجمعين

00:00:46.860 --> 00:00:49.860
نبينا محمد وعلى آله وصحبه

00:00:49.860 --> 00:00:51.860
والتابعين ومن تبعهم بإحسان

00:00:51.860 --> 00:00:53.860
إلى يوم الدين وبعد

00:00:53.860 --> 00:00:56.860
We commence by praising Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:00:56.860 --> 00:01:00.860
sending blessings and salutations upon Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:01:00.860 --> 00:01:03.860
We ask Allah to bless him and his entire household

00:01:03.860 --> 00:01:05.860
and to bless all his companions

00:01:05.860 --> 00:01:07.860
and to bless all those who have struggled

00:01:07.860 --> 00:01:09.860
and strived to protect this deen

00:01:09.860 --> 00:01:11.860
learn it, put it into practice

00:01:11.860 --> 00:01:14.860
convey it to others in a way that it has got to us today

00:01:14.860 --> 00:01:16.860
and we thank Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:01:16.860 --> 00:01:18.860
for being chosen to be from amongst

00:01:18.860 --> 00:01:21.860
the followers of Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:01:21.860 --> 00:01:23.860
and at the same time we ask him to grant

00:01:23.860 --> 00:01:25.860
our children steadfastness

00:01:25.860 --> 00:01:28.860
to use us as well to convey the message to others

00:01:28.860 --> 00:01:30.860
Beloved brothers and sisters

00:01:30.860 --> 00:01:33.860
we had spoken yesterday about how the first people

00:01:33.860 --> 00:01:35.860
of Madinah Munawwara had accepted Islam

00:01:35.860 --> 00:01:38.860
and we made mention of the names of six of them

00:01:38.860 --> 00:01:41.860
before I continue with that it's important to make mention

00:01:41.860 --> 00:01:45.860
of the marriage of Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:01:45.860 --> 00:01:49.860
after the death of his wife Khadija binti Khuwalid

00:01:49.860 --> 00:01:51.860
radiallahu anha

00:01:51.860 --> 00:01:54.860
she was the mother of all his children who were alive

00:01:54.860 --> 00:01:57.860
and she was the mother

00:01:57.860 --> 00:02:00.860
and at the same time the one who was the pillar of support

00:02:00.860 --> 00:02:03.860
at the time of need of Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:02:03.860 --> 00:02:05.860
when revelation first came down

00:02:05.860 --> 00:02:07.860
so she looked after the children

00:02:07.860 --> 00:02:09.860
and she was a wife

00:02:09.860 --> 00:02:12.860
a very big comfort at the same time

00:02:12.860 --> 00:02:16.860
and she maintained the home in a very beautiful way

00:02:16.860 --> 00:02:20.860
never is there mention of a single dispute

00:02:20.860 --> 00:02:22.860
between Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:02:22.860 --> 00:02:25.860
and Khadija binti Khuwalid radiallahu anha

00:02:25.860 --> 00:02:28.860
so after her death

00:02:28.860 --> 00:02:30.860
may Allah be pleased with her

00:02:30.860 --> 00:02:33.860
Khawla binti Hakim who was the wife of

00:02:33.860 --> 00:02:36.860
Uthman ibn Madh'un radiallahu anha

00:02:36.860 --> 00:02:41.860
she was noticing that the home of the prophet sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:02:41.860 --> 00:02:43.860
is void of a female

00:02:43.860 --> 00:02:45.860
and the children are quite small

00:02:45.860 --> 00:02:47.860
and she suggested to him

00:02:47.860 --> 00:02:50.860
Ya Rasulallah sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:02:50.860 --> 00:02:52.860
don't you want to get married

00:02:52.860 --> 00:02:54.860
and he made mention of Khadija

00:02:54.860 --> 00:02:57.860
and he always made mention of Khadija radiallahu anha

00:02:57.860 --> 00:02:59.860
so much so that he kept a good link

00:02:59.860 --> 00:03:03.860
with all her friends even later on

00:03:03.860 --> 00:03:06.860
he used to send for them a little bit of food

00:03:06.860 --> 00:03:08.860
or he used to send for them a gift

00:03:08.860 --> 00:03:10.860
or he used to get very happy

00:03:10.860 --> 00:03:11.860
when they used to come and visit

00:03:11.860 --> 00:03:14.860
even during his time in Medina Munawwara

00:03:14.860 --> 00:03:15.860
may Allah sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:03:15.860 --> 00:03:17.860
make us from amongst those

00:03:17.860 --> 00:03:19.860
who can respect our in-laws

00:03:19.860 --> 00:03:20.860
today subhanallah

00:03:20.860 --> 00:03:22.860
we have people who run very far away

00:03:22.860 --> 00:03:24.860
and they don't want to know

00:03:24.860 --> 00:03:25.860
in fact I to this day

00:03:25.860 --> 00:03:29.860
don't understand why the term in-law is used

00:03:29.860 --> 00:03:33.860
that term law normally refers to big problems

00:03:33.860 --> 00:03:34.860
when you have a big issue

00:03:34.860 --> 00:03:36.860
then you call in the lawyers and so on

00:03:36.860 --> 00:03:38.860
Allah sallallahu alayhi wa sallam protect us

00:03:38.860 --> 00:03:40.860
and grant us all goodness and ease

00:03:40.860 --> 00:03:42.860
so Rasulullah sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:03:42.860 --> 00:03:45.860
he had a suggestion made to him

00:03:45.860 --> 00:03:47.860
by Khawla binti Hakim radiallahu anha

00:03:47.860 --> 00:03:50.860
she said I suggest that you get married

00:03:50.860 --> 00:03:51.860
he says to whom

00:03:51.860 --> 00:03:54.860
so she said you can marry a virgin

00:03:54.860 --> 00:03:55.860
or you can marry a non-virgin

00:03:55.860 --> 00:03:57.860
if you would like to marry a non-virgin

00:03:57.860 --> 00:03:59.860
I am suggesting to you to marry

00:03:59.860 --> 00:04:02.860
Sauda binti Zam'ah radiallahu anha

00:04:02.860 --> 00:04:06.860
a very poor lady who was married already

00:04:06.860 --> 00:04:10.860
and her husband had passed away

00:04:10.860 --> 00:04:13.860
she was one of those who had gone to Abyssinia

00:04:13.860 --> 00:04:16.860
on the Hijra and on the return

00:04:16.860 --> 00:04:18.860
her husband had passed away

00:04:18.860 --> 00:04:20.860
and she was a person whose family

00:04:20.860 --> 00:04:22.860
were made up of mushriks

00:04:22.860 --> 00:04:25.860
she had accepted Islam at the very beginning

00:04:25.860 --> 00:04:28.860
she was persecuted to a great degree

00:04:28.860 --> 00:04:30.860
she had had her own children

00:04:30.860 --> 00:04:31.860
and she was from one of those

00:04:31.860 --> 00:04:34.860
who really needed protection

00:04:34.860 --> 00:04:36.860
and she really needed to be saved

00:04:36.860 --> 00:04:38.860
from the clutches of her own brothers

00:04:38.860 --> 00:04:40.860
who were mushriks

00:04:40.860 --> 00:04:42.860
her father was not that bad

00:04:42.860 --> 00:04:43.860
although he was a mushrik

00:04:43.860 --> 00:04:45.860
but his relation with her was not so bad

00:04:45.860 --> 00:04:47.860
and she suggested

00:04:47.860 --> 00:04:49.860
meaning Khawla binti Hakim radiallahu anha

00:04:49.860 --> 00:04:51.860
says that is a good woman

00:04:51.860 --> 00:04:53.860
she is a widow and you can marry her

00:04:53.860 --> 00:04:55.860
and the other one if you would like

00:04:55.860 --> 00:04:56.860
to marry a virgin

00:04:56.860 --> 00:04:57.860
then you can marry the daughter

00:04:57.860 --> 00:04:58.860
of your best friend

00:04:58.860 --> 00:05:00.860
although she is very young right now

00:05:00.860 --> 00:05:03.860
but as was the norm at that time

00:05:03.860 --> 00:05:05.860
this is important that we listen to this

00:05:05.860 --> 00:05:07.860
because many people claim that

00:05:07.860 --> 00:05:08.860
Muhammad sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:05:08.860 --> 00:05:09.860
married a child

00:05:09.860 --> 00:05:10.860
I seek refuge with Allah

00:05:10.860 --> 00:05:12.860
Wallahi we need to understand

00:05:12.860 --> 00:05:15.860
the norms of every community and society

00:05:15.860 --> 00:05:17.860
up to this day you have people

00:05:17.860 --> 00:05:19.860
in the Indo-Pak subcontinent

00:05:19.860 --> 00:05:20.860
that I know about

00:05:20.860 --> 00:05:23.860
and I am sure in other places of the world as well

00:05:23.860 --> 00:05:25.860
whom as soon as the child is born

00:05:25.860 --> 00:05:28.860
they say this child we fixing up with that child

00:05:28.860 --> 00:05:29.860
and it is done

00:05:29.860 --> 00:05:30.860
and it is an agreement by mouth

00:05:30.860 --> 00:05:32.860
and when they grow up nowadays

00:05:32.860 --> 00:05:34.860
you find people breaking that

00:05:34.860 --> 00:05:36.860
but there was a time when they never ever broke that

00:05:36.860 --> 00:05:38.860
if the father said this it was that

00:05:38.860 --> 00:05:41.860
they were more or less married at child birth

00:05:41.860 --> 00:05:43.860
and later on they only got to live together

00:05:43.860 --> 00:05:46.860
that does not make them bad in any way

00:05:46.860 --> 00:05:47.860
it was just the culture

00:05:47.860 --> 00:05:49.860
and it still is the culture in so many places

00:05:49.860 --> 00:05:51.860
where young age they say

00:05:51.860 --> 00:05:52.860
okay this one fixed up with that one

00:05:52.860 --> 00:05:55.860
it is just that the world has progressed at the moment

00:05:55.860 --> 00:05:59.860
and communications has become so simple and easy

00:05:59.860 --> 00:06:03.860
that we tend to have a much more broader choice today

00:06:03.860 --> 00:06:05.860
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:06:05.860 --> 00:06:07.860
grant us a deeper understanding

00:06:07.860 --> 00:06:09.860
and at the same time we tend to be

00:06:09.860 --> 00:06:15.860
a little bit more free of the choices of our own parents

00:06:15.860 --> 00:06:17.860
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us understanding

00:06:17.860 --> 00:06:19.860
so there was a suggestion

00:06:19.860 --> 00:06:21.860
and Muhammad sallallahu alaihi wasallam said

00:06:21.860 --> 00:06:23.860
you know what speak to Sawda

00:06:23.860 --> 00:06:25.860
subhanallah look at his choice

00:06:25.860 --> 00:06:27.860
he had children and he had

00:06:27.860 --> 00:06:30.860
subhanallah children to be looked after

00:06:30.860 --> 00:06:33.860
and he was looking for someone who would also be able to comfort him

00:06:33.860 --> 00:06:36.860
be a mother and a wife at the same time

00:06:36.860 --> 00:06:39.860
and this was the woman whom he had selected

00:06:39.860 --> 00:06:43.860
and he had chosen or he had given preference to

00:06:43.860 --> 00:06:45.860
so what had happened

00:06:45.860 --> 00:06:48.860
Khawla binti Hakim radiallahu anha

00:06:48.860 --> 00:06:50.860
went to Sawda

00:06:50.860 --> 00:06:53.860
she was married to al-Sakran ibn Amr before

00:06:53.860 --> 00:06:55.860
and he passed away radiallahu anha

00:06:55.860 --> 00:06:56.860
what a good man

00:06:56.860 --> 00:06:58.860
and he had passed away

00:06:58.860 --> 00:07:02.860
and now Khawla binti Hakim says to Sawda

00:07:02.860 --> 00:07:04.860
I want to give you some good news

00:07:04.860 --> 00:07:07.860
the Prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam has sent me to you

00:07:07.860 --> 00:07:09.860
asking you for marriage

00:07:09.860 --> 00:07:11.860
meaning your hand in marriage

00:07:11.860 --> 00:07:13.860
what do you have to say

00:07:13.860 --> 00:07:15.860
she was obviously shocked

00:07:15.860 --> 00:07:17.860
she was in awe

00:07:17.860 --> 00:07:18.860
she couldn't believe it

00:07:18.860 --> 00:07:20.860
she had suffered and suffered so much

00:07:20.860 --> 00:07:23.860
the wives that the Prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam chose

00:07:23.860 --> 00:07:26.860
were those who had suffered a lot

00:07:26.860 --> 00:07:28.860
and they were in need of protection

00:07:28.860 --> 00:07:32.860
they were basically left more or less at the clutches of the enemy

00:07:32.860 --> 00:07:35.860
and they were being oppressed in so many ways

00:07:35.860 --> 00:07:39.860
so she this was a sigh of relief for her

00:07:39.860 --> 00:07:41.860
she said look alhamdulillah

00:07:41.860 --> 00:07:42.860
yes I am okay with it

00:07:42.860 --> 00:07:44.860
but you need to speak to my father

00:07:44.860 --> 00:07:47.860
imagine the father being a non-Muslim

00:07:47.860 --> 00:07:49.860
being one of the mushrik of Quraish

00:07:49.860 --> 00:07:53.860
still Sawda binti Zam'ah radiallahu anha says

00:07:53.860 --> 00:07:55.860
go and speak to my father

00:07:55.860 --> 00:08:00.860
so when the message went to the father of this particular woman

00:08:00.860 --> 00:08:03.860
Ummul Mumineen Sawda binti Zam'ah radiallahu anha

00:08:03.860 --> 00:08:04.860
who was an elderly woman

00:08:04.860 --> 00:08:06.860
she wasn't a young girl

00:08:06.860 --> 00:08:07.860
he was very happy

00:08:07.860 --> 00:08:09.860
he was an old man who was a mushrik

00:08:09.860 --> 00:08:11.860
and he was one of those of Makkah

00:08:11.860 --> 00:08:12.860
but he was happy to him

00:08:12.860 --> 00:08:15.860
his daughter was getting fixed in the right direction

00:08:15.860 --> 00:08:16.860
and she would be looked after

00:08:16.860 --> 00:08:20.860
by the man who shares the same belief as her

00:08:20.860 --> 00:08:21.860
and this was something that he looked at

00:08:21.860 --> 00:08:23.860
and thereafter subhanallah

00:08:23.860 --> 00:08:25.860
they ended up getting married

00:08:25.860 --> 00:08:27.860
it is reported in the tenth year of Hijra

00:08:27.860 --> 00:08:28.860
which was the same year

00:08:28.860 --> 00:08:32.860
that Khadija binti Khuwailid radiallahu anha had passed away

00:08:32.860 --> 00:08:34.860
and Sawda binti Zam'ah was such a happy woman

00:08:34.860 --> 00:08:38.860
she looked after the children of Rasulullah sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:08:38.860 --> 00:08:39.860
to a certain extent

00:08:39.860 --> 00:08:40.860
she was within the home

00:08:40.860 --> 00:08:41.860
she provided comfort

00:08:41.860 --> 00:08:46.860
and she says that never ever did we have any issues or difficulties

00:08:46.860 --> 00:08:48.860
she was in awe of this man

00:08:48.860 --> 00:08:49.860
what a great man

00:08:49.860 --> 00:08:51.860
she learned so much from him

00:08:51.860 --> 00:08:54.860
she was protected from her own family members

00:08:54.860 --> 00:08:57.860
and the others who had intended to harm her

00:08:57.860 --> 00:09:00.860
this was the marriage of Rasulullah sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:09:00.860 --> 00:09:03.860
after Khadija binti Khuwailid radiallahu anha

00:09:03.860 --> 00:09:05.860
now we move further

00:09:05.860 --> 00:09:10.860
and we go back to the six names of those six who had accepted Islam

00:09:10.860 --> 00:09:12.860
after coming from Madina Munawwara

00:09:12.860 --> 00:09:15.860
when the Prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam met them at the festival

00:09:15.860 --> 00:09:18.860
the names, we just mentioned them again so that we know

00:09:18.860 --> 00:09:19.860
we mentioned them yesterday

00:09:19.860 --> 00:09:22.860
As'ad bnu Zurara radiallahu anha

00:09:22.860 --> 00:09:25.860
these names when we hear them wallahi they should make our hair stand

00:09:25.860 --> 00:09:30.860
because these were those who sacrificed at the very beginning of Islam

00:09:30.860 --> 00:09:31.860
they sacrificed

00:09:31.860 --> 00:09:34.860
and they were the ones who gave their lives

00:09:34.860 --> 00:09:41.860
and they were the ones whom Allah used to change the entire geopolitical situation

00:09:41.860 --> 00:09:43.860
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala protect us

00:09:43.860 --> 00:09:46.860
As'ad bnu Zurara radiallahu anha

00:09:46.860 --> 00:09:48.860
he wasn't such an old man

00:09:48.860 --> 00:09:50.860
he was from Khazraj

00:09:50.860 --> 00:09:52.860
then we have A'uth ibn al-Harith

00:09:52.860 --> 00:09:56.860
and Rafi' ibn Malik, Qutbah ibn Amir, Uqbah ibn Amir

00:09:56.860 --> 00:09:58.860
and Jabir ibn Abdullah

00:09:58.860 --> 00:09:59.860
may Allah be pleased with all of them

00:09:59.860 --> 00:10:03.860
these people when Rasulullah sallallahu alaihi wasallam met them

00:10:03.860 --> 00:10:04.860
in Mina

00:10:04.860 --> 00:10:06.860
and he told them where are you from?

00:10:06.860 --> 00:10:08.860
they said that we are from Madinah Munawarah

00:10:08.860 --> 00:10:09.860
they said Yathrib

00:10:09.860 --> 00:10:12.860
Yathrib was the name of the place at that particular time

00:10:12.860 --> 00:10:13.860
and what had happened is

00:10:13.860 --> 00:10:15.860
he spoke to them

00:10:15.860 --> 00:10:17.860
can I speak to you for a little while?

00:10:17.860 --> 00:10:18.860
yes

00:10:18.860 --> 00:10:21.860
I mentioned yesterday the diplomacy of Rasulullah sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:10:21.860 --> 00:10:22.860
he spoke to them

00:10:22.860 --> 00:10:24.860
told them what Quraysh was doing

00:10:24.860 --> 00:10:25.860
told them the message

00:10:25.860 --> 00:10:27.860
the message of Tawheed

00:10:27.860 --> 00:10:30.860
the message of worshipping one Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:10:30.860 --> 00:10:31.860
your maker

00:10:31.860 --> 00:10:32.860
that's who you worship

00:10:32.860 --> 00:10:35.860
that is the prime message that he always delivered

00:10:35.860 --> 00:10:38.860
and he told them much more about Islam

00:10:38.860 --> 00:10:39.860
they accepted it readily

00:10:39.860 --> 00:10:41.860
because amongst themselves they said

00:10:41.860 --> 00:10:43.860
we know the Jews in Madinah Munawarah

00:10:43.860 --> 00:10:45.860
always speak about life after death

00:10:45.860 --> 00:10:46.860
they speak about heaven

00:10:46.860 --> 00:10:47.860
they speak about hell

00:10:47.860 --> 00:10:49.860
and they always speak about the fact that

00:10:49.860 --> 00:10:52.860
there is a prophet who is about to come to Madinah

00:10:52.860 --> 00:10:55.860
there is a prophet who is about to come

00:10:55.860 --> 00:10:57.860
and appear at the moment

00:10:57.860 --> 00:10:58.860
his time is here

00:10:58.860 --> 00:10:59.860
that is why we are all here

00:10:59.860 --> 00:11:00.860
the Jews used to say

00:11:00.860 --> 00:11:01.860
subhanallah

00:11:01.860 --> 00:11:04.860
so they immediately accepted the message

00:11:04.860 --> 00:11:05.860
they were very very happy

00:11:05.860 --> 00:11:07.860
and Rasulullah sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:11:07.860 --> 00:11:09.860
gave them some advice

00:11:09.860 --> 00:11:11.860
they had left to Madinah Munawarah

00:11:11.860 --> 00:11:13.860
and they were the first people

00:11:13.860 --> 00:11:17.860
who actively started talking about Islam in Madinah

00:11:17.860 --> 00:11:18.860
and they started spreading it

00:11:18.860 --> 00:11:20.860
remember Al-Aws and Khazraj

00:11:20.860 --> 00:11:23.860
these were two warring tribes

00:11:23.860 --> 00:11:25.860
that were present in Madinah Munawarah

00:11:25.860 --> 00:11:26.860
they fought so much

00:11:26.860 --> 00:11:29.860
we made mention of the war of Buath yesterday

00:11:29.860 --> 00:11:31.860
where a lot of their leaders were killed

