00:36:29.210 --> 00:36:31.210
select from amongst you 12 men

00:36:31.210 --> 00:36:33.210
who will be like the caretakers

00:36:33.210 --> 00:36:36.210
people who will look after the Muslims in Madinah Munawwarah

00:36:36.210 --> 00:36:38.210
Subhanallah they selected 12 men

00:36:38.210 --> 00:36:40.210
their names are there

00:36:40.210 --> 00:36:42.210
there were people from Al-Khazraj most of them

00:36:42.210 --> 00:36:44.210
and a few from Aws

00:36:44.210 --> 00:36:47.210
and these 12 their duty was

00:36:47.210 --> 00:36:50.210
to take care of the Muslims in Madinah Munawwarah

00:36:50.210 --> 00:36:52.210
and to look after them and so on

00:36:52.210 --> 00:36:54.210
and in the meantime

00:36:54.210 --> 00:36:58.210
