00:36:58.210 --> 00:37:01.210
Shaytan announced to Quraysh

00:37:01.210 --> 00:37:03.210
in Mina

00:37:03.210 --> 00:37:05.210
Shaytan announced to Quraysh

00:37:05.210 --> 00:37:09.210
