00:37:09.210 --> 00:37:10.210
by Muhammad

00:37:10.210 --> 00:37:12.210
and the people of Madinah

00:37:12.210 --> 00:37:13.210
the people of Yathrib

00:37:13.210 --> 00:37:16.210
are pledging an allegiance with him

00:37:16.210 --> 00:37:18.210
so Rasulullah صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:37:18.210 --> 00:37:19.210
at that particular moment

00:37:19.210 --> 00:37:21.210
told these people go back to your caravans

00:37:21.210 --> 00:37:23.210
and you know just disperse

00:37:23.210 --> 00:37:26.210
so it was cut without further ado

00:37:26.210 --> 00:37:28.210
the meeting was closed

00:37:28.210 --> 00:37:29.210
and they had returned

