so Al-Abbas says

00:38:24.210 --> 00:38:26.210
I don't recognize these people

00:38:26.210 --> 00:38:28.210
but he knew the people of Medina

00:38:28.210 --> 00:38:29.210
the older generation

00:38:29.210 --> 00:38:32.210
so when Quraysh met

00:38:32.210 --> 00:38:33.210
the people of Aws and Khazraj

00:38:33.210 --> 00:38:34.210
the following morning

