00:38:52.210 --> 00:38:53.210
and subhanallah

00:38:53.210 --> 00:38:54.210
the old people are saying

00:38:54.210 --> 00:38:55.210
wallahi

00:38:55.210 --> 00:38:56.210
nothing of this nature happened

