00:40:50.110 --> 00:40:51.110
no ways

00:40:51.110 --> 00:40:52.110
not at all

00:40:52.110 --> 00:40:53.110
so they took

00:40:53.110 --> 00:40:54.110
Umm Salama away

00:40:54.110 --> 00:40:56.110
with Salama

00:40:56.110 --> 00:40:57.110
and Abu Salama

